Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:29.50,0:00:33.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,#26 回歸憂國之路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.87,0:00:36.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,空襲又開始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:37.64,0:00:40.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有人攔截到船員的通訊嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:40.38,0:00:41.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.48,0:00:44.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,完全沒有可以竊聽的電波
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:44.58,0:00:45.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,塔奇克馬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:45.75,0:00:49.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在立刻收集電腦空間內的可使用區域
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:49.32,0:00:53.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,確保能夠傳送300萬人記憶和Ghost的空間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:53.12,0:00:56.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哎？這麼突然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.29,0:00:58.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒時間了，動作快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:58.13,0:00:58.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是，可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:59.00,0:01:01.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這種事情，能辦到嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:01.57,0:01:02.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:02.87,0:01:05.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是我找不到其它可以拯救難民的方法了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.00,0:01:06.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜託你們了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.97,0:01:08.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,了...瞭解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.98,0:01:16.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我剛剛叫支援AI在電腦空間確保可使用的區域
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:16.51,0:01:18.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,準備完畢之後，就開始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:18.78,0:01:19.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多謝相助
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:20.19,0:01:22.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,借由將Ghost整個傳送到網絡上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:22.72,0:01:25.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,假設我們可以活下來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:25.49,0:01:27.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那沒有電子腦化的人怎麼辦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:29.56,0:01:34.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對親友當中有這類人的人來說\N應該很難接受這個結論
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:35.50,0:01:37.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們大概會對我感到失望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.87,0:01:39.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,自行離開出島吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.01,0:01:42.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在這種狀況之下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.77,0:01:46.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,指導者的任務常常既重大又充滿不安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.21,0:01:50.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,站在不得不指引多數人的立場上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.82,0:01:53.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有時會因情況被迫做出獨斷的決定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.99,0:01:56.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這些，他們應該也會瞭解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.62,0:02:00.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果真是這樣，就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.16,0:02:05.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,塔奇克馬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.36,0:02:07.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,給我到少校那邊的最短路線
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.50,0:02:08.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,巴特先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.73,0:02:10.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不是往大橋去了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.77,0:02:12.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要去找少校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.57,0:02:15.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,巴特先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.81,0:02:17.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,通訊斷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.95,0:02:27.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,核導彈會不會趁空襲後的混亂發射呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.75,0:02:30.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從潛艇幾乎沒有通訊的狀況來看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.96,0:02:33.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,發射時間或許早就決定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.66,0:02:35.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼說……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.49,0:02:39.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從宙斯盾艦的距離以及微機械散佈的時機來觀察
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.96,0:02:43.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,AM 10:00 這個時間很可疑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.20,0:02:49.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各位，你們實際上是怎麼想的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.24,0:02:51.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把難民的記憶上傳到網絡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.88,0:02:54.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的能夠維持Ghost存在嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.32,0:03:01.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,記憶雖然是生命活動很重要的要素
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.52,0:03:04.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過，沒有Ghost就只是單純的數據
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.56,0:03:08.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是，少校不是把一線\N希望寄托在這上面嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.66,0:03:12.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這我也知道，可是這實在\N是很亂來的命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.73,0:03:14.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也是這麼想的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.43,0:03:18.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是繼續做下去，也沒辦法\N救巴特先生他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.70,0:03:22.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因此，我覺得應該不\N要理會少校的命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.41,0:03:24.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 咦？你在說什麼啊！\N- 不懂你的意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.44,0:03:25.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 那該怎麼辦？\N- 我做不到啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.98,0:03:28.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼樣了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.68,0:03:29.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.18,0:03:32.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,完全不回應我的呼叫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.45,0:03:36.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,熱線明明是通的……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.19,0:03:38.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這就表示……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.41,0:03:39.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.46,0:03:41.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不甘心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.09,0:03:47.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我確實是國會解散重新改選時打選戰的廣告牌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.13,0:03:50.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過，我從未被如此刻薄的對待過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.41,0:03:57.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,高倉既然做到這個地步
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.64,0:03:59.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也要用我的方式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.64,0:04:01.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,收拾這個局勢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.61,0:04:03.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,您要跟哪裏聯繫呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.82,0:04:10.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,成功了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.69,0:04:12.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是第8個了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.76,0:04:15.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這種運算，我可是高手中的高手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.83,0:04:20.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再搞定一個，就肯定能在\N導彈軌道上布下彈幕了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.87,0:04:23.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然照你說的，違反少校的命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.90,0:04:27.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過，進行衛星墜落作業\N真的是正確的選擇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.04,0:04:29.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,唔……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.34,0:04:30.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.44,0:04:32.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明明進行得很順利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.91,0:04:34.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.91,0:04:39.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這說不定是搭載我們AI的衛星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.75,0:04:41.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哎？……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.49,0:04:42.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼，為什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.52,0:04:44.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是美帝的衛星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.85,0:04:45.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.56,0:04:52.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們看來好像是借用了\N從日本發射的美帝衛星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.40,0:04:54.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.40,0:04:58.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,結果安保條約締不締結\N還不是得聽那些傢伙的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.80,0:05:02.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少校為什麼要把我們的AI放在那種地方？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.01,0:05:07.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,或許是想反過來\N對美帝搞諜報之類的工作吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.01,0:05:11.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然搞不清楚那麼多\N但這下可傷腦筋了……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.75,0:05:13.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已經沒有時間了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.36,0:05:25.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,石川先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.66,0:05:26.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.90,0:05:31.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我必須跟大家一起去某個地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.27,0:05:33.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.27,0:05:37.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.88,0:05:39.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.14,0:05:40.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.28,0:05:42.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少校他們的事情就拜託了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.58,0:05:43.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.55,0:05:47.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.69,0:05:50.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接下來就真的是一個人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.29,0:05:56.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.30,0:05:58.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在哪裏？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.17,0:06:09.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,久世
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.21,0:06:10.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.34,0:06:12.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你會折紙鶴嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.01,0:06:14.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,紙鶴？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.18,0:06:15.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.35,0:06:17.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且只用一隻左手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.28,0:06:23.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要使用控制軟體\N任何人都會折的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.55,0:06:25.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不是這個意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.43,0:06:29.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你會折嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.19,0:06:31.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只用左手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.83,0:06:32.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在可以了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.96,0:06:36.44,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\pos(75,228)}{\fad(300,400)}I do
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.16,0:06:36.14,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\pos(75,240)}{\fad(300,400)}作詞：Ilaria
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.36,0:06:36.24,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\pos(75,252)}{\fad(300,400)}作曲：菅野洋子(Yoko kanno)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.56,0:06:36.34,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\pos(75,264)}{\fad(300,400)}演唱：Ilaria graziano
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.44,0:06:38.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你也是依靠孤獨生活下去的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.57,0:06:40.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,名字呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.64,0:06:43.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,之前一直沒問，叫什麼名字呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.34,0:06:44.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,忘了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.38,0:06:47.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,假名倒是有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.31,0:06:49.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這點你也是一樣吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.31,0:06:55.44,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Nell' illusione ho creduto alla mia forza inesorabile\N在夢幻中，我相信自己無畏的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.81,0:06:50.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說的也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.05,0:06:55.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難民幫我取了好幾個名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.44,0:07:01.04,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,e inevitabilmente sono diventata debole\N卻軟弱到無法逃避
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.92,0:06:58.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我雖然是為了拯救他們\N才和他們一起行動的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.52,0:07:01.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但也許只是為了填補孤獨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.04,0:07:06.34,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,ora sento gli eventi si transformano e so gia\N我現在所能感知的，是那變換的時空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.64,0:07:03.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,才跟他們在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.00,0:07:06.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是到最後還是沒能填補
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.14,0:07:16.64,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,di emozioni che aprono ricordi lontani\N強烈的感情喚起久遠的記憶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.14,0:07:09.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為即使被人依賴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.43,0:07:11.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,自己卻無法依賴別人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.04,0:07:16.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你有可以交心的對象嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.84,0:07:23.08,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,nell'anima ritrovo la speranza che nel corpo stanco ormai\N靈魂重新感受希望，而精疲力竭的身體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.31,0:07:18.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也不能說是沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.52,0:07:29.54,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,ha smesso di vibrare come un fuoco spento dal mio pianto\N卻如同淚水澆熄的火焰般停止跳躍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.71,0:07:24.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.08,0:07:29.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我一直……都在尋找
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.54,0:07:35.44,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,tra le mani un filo d'acqua portero con me e\N用雙手汲取，哪怕是一掬水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.13,0:07:42.74,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,nel deserto un filo d'erba sopravvivera\N沙漠裏就會有些許的草生存下來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.03,0:07:39.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒事的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.86,0:07:42.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,導彈不會飛到大橋附近來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.74,0:07:44.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要慌，快點過去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.34,0:07:47.31,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I do,I do
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.83,0:07:52.06,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,gridare contro gli occhi spenti e gelidi\N我對著他寒冷似冰的眼睛哭喊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.19,0:07:58.42,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,per essere sempre di piu\N總有一天會比現在更好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.54,0:08:02.10,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I do,I do
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.28,0:08:06.55,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,oltrepassare mondi inespugnabili\N超越磐石般的世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.75,0:08:12.78,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,senza temere nulla piu...\N為了不再畏懼虛無
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.03,0:08:16.65,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I do,I do
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.21,0:08:21.17,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,emeregere dal fondo per lottare e poi\N掙扎著想從沉淪中飛昇起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.41,0:08:27.55,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,salire in alto piu che mai\N升至前所未有的高度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.65,0:08:31.28,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I do,I do
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.51,0:08:35.61,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,guardare nel futuro e sorridere\N望著未來而微笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.04,0:08:41.09,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,con una nuova identita\N與全新的自我一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.59,0:08:52.00,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,fino a quando il sole sorgera...\N待到太陽升起之時……
