Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.08,0:09:47.39,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,まっかに流れる 僕の血潮\N我的热血鲜红地流淌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.46,0:09:51.76,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,みみずだって おけらだって\N不管是蚯蚓还是蝼蛄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.83,0:09:53.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼會有這種事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.83,0:09:53.63,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,あめんぼだって\N或者是水蝇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.70,0:09:59.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們大家一定\N是有Ghost的……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.70,0:09:59.33,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,みんなみんな 生きているんだ\N我们大家都活着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.40,0:10:02.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了，普路托？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.40,0:10:02.93,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,友達なんだ\N都是好朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.81,0:10:07.68,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,ぼくらはみんな 生きている\N我们大家都活着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.75,0:10:11.70,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,生きているから わらうんだ\N因为活着才会欢笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.78,0:10:15.62,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,ぼくらはみんな 生きている\N我们大家都活着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.78,0:10:15.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,上傳：全體塔奇克馬的記憶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.69,0:10:19.92,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,生きているから うれしいんだ\N因为活着才会快乐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.99,0:10:27.56,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,手のひらを太陽に 透かしてみれば\N让阳光透过你的手掌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.63,0:10:34.90,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,まっかに流れる 僕の血潮\N我的热血鲜红地流淌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.97,0:10:39.50,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,とんぼだって かえるだって\N不管是蜻蜓还是青蛙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.58,0:10:43.81,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,みつばちだって\N或者是蜜蜂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.88,0:10:48.84,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,みんなみんな 生きているんだ 友だち...\N我们大家都活着，都是好朋友……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.09,0:10:53.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼回事，普路托？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.39,0:10:55.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,發生什麼事了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.16,0:10:59.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看樣子，塔奇克馬跟衛星\N一起去撞核彈了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.00,0:11:01.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,塔奇克馬？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.70,0:11:04.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阻止了最糟糕的事態發生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.77,0:11:05.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.20,0:11:09.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在的情況，我不太瞭解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.47,0:11:14.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,似乎因為部下的犧牲\N阻止了核導彈的發射
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.35,0:11:15.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,部下的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.75,0:11:18.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,先不說這個，剛剛您提到的……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.95,0:11:24.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.32,0:11:27.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,導彈毀了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.83,0:11:30.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.36,0:11:35.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,反正茅葺的行動將\N促使冷戰構造完成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.67,0:11:40.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過，這樣一來他就當不上英雄了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.14,0:11:45.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個爆炸是……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.58,0:11:46.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.58,0:11:49.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽到了塔奇克馬的歌聲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.28,0:11:51.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那些小鬼幫我們擋下來了麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.57,0:12:09.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.67,0:12:10.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知道為什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.97,0:12:14.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,AI採取了跟我的命令不同的行動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.04,0:12:20.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少校，你沒事嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.88,0:12:21.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,塔奇克馬它們……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.82,0:12:33.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,課長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.79,0:12:35.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果總理聯繫的地方……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.83,0:12:37.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.33,0:12:41.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過，現在必須先抓住\N官房長官與合田
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.57,0:12:46.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這件事也有可能在我們\N有生之年都不能公開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.07,0:12:49.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,先迅速進行，事後處理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.74,0:12:50.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.21,0:12:56.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,進來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.48,0:13:01.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,官房長官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.12,0:13:04.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,您應該知道我們到這裏來的理由吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.89,0:13:06.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是政變
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.56,0:13:09.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也是以戰爭為借口的屠殺行為
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.86,0:13:12.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我無法眼睜睜看著他們用核彈自爆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.06,0:13:15.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,根本就沒有這回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.37,0:13:19.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,寫下這個劇本的應該是您\N還有內廳的合田
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.70,0:13:20.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,合田？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.41,0:13:26.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只是在考慮國家未來的前提下\N提前締結新安保條約而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.24,0:13:28.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是一場跟難民之間的戰爭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.85,0:13:31.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,長官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.12,0:13:36.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接下來，您將在非公開狀態下\N接受嚴格查問
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.22,0:13:38.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我早就有心理準備了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.42,0:13:39.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說起來……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.59,0:13:43.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你比我預料的更像個女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.96,0:13:47.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然我不知道你感情用事\N跑去向哪邊求助
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.30,0:13:51.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但這個國家不依靠美帝\N是無法存活下去的……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.30,0:13:54.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,您恐怕有什麼誤會吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.27,0:13:59.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,似乎核彈沒有爆炸呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.44,0:14:00.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼辦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.78,0:14:02.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要發射第二枚嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.71,0:14:03.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.68,0:14:08.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,確認從東北方南下的飛機\N屬於哪一方再說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.39,0:14:12.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是機身上如果\N有八一徽標的話……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.36,0:14:20.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一身獨立，而至一國獨立
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.36,0:14:20.66,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,出自福澤諭吉《勸學》，日本當代政治名言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.60,0:14:27.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我自始至終，就是這樣思考和行動的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.14,0:14:32.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,茅葺政權將一如既往\N在同美帝、美俄聯盟、中國
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.64,0:14:36.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以及亞洲、E.U(歐盟)各國\N保持同等政治距離之下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.91,0:14:38.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,依照獨自的判斷行動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.98,0:14:42.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,摸索在聯合國的協調路線
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.40,0:14:57.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,航空自衛軍的秘密部隊麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.90,0:15:00.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已經確認到日本方面的意思了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.34,0:15:01.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,撤退
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.67,0:15:04.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請帶他走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.34,0:15:05.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.25,0:15:13.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總理命令我們來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.98,0:15:15.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請快點上來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.39,0:15:16.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.89,0:15:18.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,站起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.92,0:15:23.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這把刀，請物歸原主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.64,0:15:35.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,齋藤、帕茲、博瑪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.51,0:15:37.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少校，你沒事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.30,0:15:38.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.51,0:15:42.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不好意思，要麻煩你們\N向自衛軍匯報詳細情況
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.31,0:15:43.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.80,0:15:58.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.51,0:16:15.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是公安9課的石川？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.65,0:16:17.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請你把那個交給我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.05,0:16:20.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.42,0:16:21.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.12,0:16:28.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要小看人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.89,0:16:32.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們9課可是最擅長打架和情報戰的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.03,0:16:39.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奴隸之國要是怠於侍奉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.64,0:16:42.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,消費之國必然會致飢餓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.44,0:16:45.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人手不足雖然讓勞動製造業獲利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.74,0:16:50.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是過度主張權力\N資本主義的血脈將會硬化
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.51,0:16:54.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我國雖然徹頭徹尾自稱是資本主義
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.38,0:16:57.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,實際卻是理想化的社會主義國家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.99,0:17:03.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要是累積了廢物\N就需要能夠操作血液分離的大腦
